# ZILFCore API

## GameObjects

- Always use `init(name:description:location:flags:)` when creating `GameObject` instances. Omit the `flags` param when empty.
- Always use dynamic member lookup when accessing dynamic state values.

## Command parsing

- Always use `init?(from:)` when finding a `Command` in the user's input.

## Flags

- Always use the correct `Flag`